            "text_Uidqpe": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h3>Shipping & Delivery</h3><p><strong>Q: How long does shipping take?</strong><br/>A: We typically process orders within 1-3 business days. Delivery times vary by location.</p><p><strong>Q: Do you offer international shipping?</strong><br/>A: Yes, we ship to select international destinations. Shipping costs and delivery times vary by country.</p><h3>Products & Care</h3><p><strong>Q: Are your products made from organic materials?</strong><br/>A: Yes, our babywear is made from certified organic cotton and modal fabrics that are gentle on sensitive skin.</p><p><strong>Q: How do I care for my organic cotton items?</strong><br/>A: We recommend washing in cold water with gentle detergent and air drying to maintain fabric quality.</p><p><strong>Q: Are HopFrog Shoes Orthopedic?</strong></p><p>HopFrog shoes <a href=\"https://www.hopfrogkids.com/blog/icerik/hopfrog-kids-3f-feelfitflex-barefoot-nedir\" target=\"_blank\">with 3F Barefoot</a> feature a special sole and ergonomic structure that allows our little ones to grow healthily and naturally, just like walking barefoot in nature.</p><p><a><strong>Q: Do the soles of your slippers cause slipping?</strong></a></p><p>All our HopFrog booties feature a special non-slip Bio Vegan® leather outsole.</p><p><a><strong>Q: Are your slippers suitable for every season?</strong></a></p><p>Designed to support the healthy foot development of our little ones, HopFrog booties are suitable for all seasons and are made from high-quality, eco-friendly materials</p><p><a><strong>Q: Do your slippers make your feet sweat?</strong></a></p><p>All HopFrog booties provide superior comfort for little feet with their OrthoFlex® (100% recycled) footbed technology. Thanks to its cellular structure, it never causes sweating. It features a non-slip special Bio Vegan® leather outsole and an eco-friendly insole that prevents bad odors. In addition, the bootie elastic is 100% natural silicone (food-safe enough for use in kitchen utensils), which does not cause sweating or odor.</p><p><a><strong>Q: Can shoes be washed in a washing machine?</strong></a></p><p>Yes, all Hopfrög Kids booties and shoes for your little one are made from washable materials (e.g., faux leather upper, Meckel stitched sole, etc.). There's not much you need to do with the shoes and booties. Simply place them in a laundry bag and wash them in the washing machine on a low-temperature, non-intensive cycle with a mild detergent, then relax and unwind. Afterwards, enjoy the benefits of a thorough cleaning by allowing them to dry and air dry completely. Please avoid exposing the shoes directly to sunlight or other heat sources during drying.</p><h3>Orders & Returns</h3><p><strong>Q: Can I modify or cancel my order?</strong><br/>A: Please contact us immediately if you need to modify your order. Once shipped, changes cannot be made.</p><p><strong>Q: What is your return policy?</strong><br/>A: We accept returns within 7 days of delivery for unworn, unwashed items in original packaging.</p><h3>Contact</h3><p><strong>Q: How can I contact customer service?</strong><br/>A: You can reach us through our contact form or email. We typically respond within 24 hours.</p>",
